{"tid":314080,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「三國」覺唔覺關羽張飛其實好累事","createTime":"2017-07-09T01:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T07:47:14.000Z","uid":81234,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ea9746ecbbda219941bf1bb86c06dac5d8db46ac","tid":314080,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T01:15:16.000Z","msg":"先以三國演義黎計<br />\n成日話咩劉備最好就係有兩兄弟幫佢手<br />\n一個 囂到死 搞到失荊州 <br />\n又成日搞事 話唔服黃忠馬超做五虎將又要人哄<br />\n<br />\n另一個 平時已經成日罵人<br />\n又日日喝酒打軍士 失徐州 <br />\n關羽死後又逼劉備伐吳報仇<br />\n<br />\n以三國志黎講<br />\n佢兩個都係累事既仆街<br />\n<br />\n睇到佢地比人隊死好爽快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68599989685ebed2415c5096810c3f72f22675b2","tid":314080,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T01:17:21.000Z","msg":"其實豬腳亮既奸計"},{"pid":"e6f823c6d1cb04b41dd6a7432f9f4b5fcb078371","tid":314080,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T01:17:37.000Z","msg":"但無佢哋劉備就發唔到圍"},{"pid":"49c1b6bad34e68ab777ca8d0afe06a7e7117f937","tid":314080,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T01:28:31.000Z","msg":"一介武抓夫衝動自大，真係冇計"},{"pid":"3ed7371e05d08e0b2bb3e83568ae8479d4f5d3ef","tid":314080,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T01:40:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但無佢哋劉備就發唔到圍</blockquote><br />\n不過天下野心之士數之不盡，劉備再搵多幾個劉表都得"},{"pid":"6c477bae381e7430242dc5b620586133999a3cbd","tid":314080,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但無佢哋劉備就發唔到圍</blockquote><br />\n唔完全係<br />\n劉備真正發圍更多係靠班荊州人入伙之後<br />\n呢兩個重要更多係佢地係劉備手下少有可以獨領一方既嫡系"},{"pid":"4baa2951712e36033f6e29bbe71c425a8d3df636","tid":314080,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:21:45.000Z","msg":"唔係關羽on9 死<br />\n蜀可能唔洗咁快滅國"},{"pid":"950504c1895bb1b0165faed0d3bf638fb3c751eb","tid":314080,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited